Blurb::
Smoothed merit function
Description::
APPS solves nonlinearly constrained problems by solving a sequence of
linearly constrained merit function-base subproblems. There are
several exact and smoothed exact penalty functions.

\c merit_max_smooth: based on smoothed \f$ \ell_\infty\f$ norm

